<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE>2012</DATELINE><TITLE>Mapping the New World of Necrotizing Enterocolitis (NEC): Review and Opinion</TITLE><BODY>A comprehensive review of necrotizing enterocolitis (NEC) is provided; including history, biological basis and frequently asked questions. In addition, a system of improved NEC classification is explained in detail (consisting of five NEC subsets and four NEC-like diseases), to aid the bedside clinician in therapy and prevention. The authors offer opinion for therapeutics in italics at the end of each definition.&#3;</BODY></TEXT>